  "Former finance professional Abhay So is chairman and managing director of Max Healthcare Institute, India's second largest listed hospital chain by revenue.",
  "Soi started his career at the erstwhile Arthur Andersen and later worked for EY and KPMG.",
  "Son got his entrepreneurial break in 2010 when he took over a struggling 650-bed hospital in Delhi and set up Radiant Life Care.",
  "Radiant was merged with Max in June 2020 and listed two months later. Private equity firm KKR retains a majority stake, while Soi has a significant minority stake."
